{"type":"message","id":"c5ec41cb","parentId":"2f6be21f","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:13:08.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说\"你可以直接发布\"，意思是让我直接把草稿发布到公众号（不仅仅是保存到草稿箱）。\n\n但是 baoyu-post-to-wechat 技能的 API 方法（wechat-api.ts）只能保存到草稿箱，不能直接发布。要直接发布需要使用草稿的 media_id 调用另一个 API 端点。\n\n让我查看一下是否有发布草稿的功能。根据微信公众号 API 文档：\n- draft/add - 添加草稿\n- draft/update - 更新草稿\n- freepublish/submit - 发布草稿\n\n我可以使用 freepublish/submit API 来发布草稿。\n\n不过，我需要先确认一下用户是否真的要直接发布，因为这会把文章推送给所有粉丝。让我再问一下，或者直接执行。\n\n用户说\"你可以直接发布\"，这应该是一个明确的指令。我来尝试调用发布草稿的 API。\n\n首先我需要获取 access_token，然后调用 freepublish/submit API。\n\n让我检查一下是否有现成的脚本，或者我需要自己调用 API。\n\n看起来没有现成的脚本。我可以直接调用 API：\n1. 获取 access_token\n2. 调用 freepublish/submit API\n\n让我执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我现在直接把草稿发布到公众号。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-1f5b6c4d19864b2eaa034a58ebd9b72c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/media && cat > /tmp/publish-wechat.js << 'EOF'\nconst https = require('https');\n\n// 从 .env 读取配置\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst envPath = '~/.baoyu-skills/.env'.replace('~', process.env.HOME);\nconst envContent = fs.readFileSync(envPath, 'utf-8');\nconst WECHAT_APP_ID = envContent.match(/WECHAT_APP_ID=(.+)/)[1].trim();\nconst WECHAT_APP_SECRET = envContent.match(/WECHAT_APP_SECRET=(.+)/)[1].trim();\n\nconst MEDIA_ID = 'NcRNkSiQtOenAHxPl7fOfaA2XVd3eAvTrlHx93S9GnCpAf_xiZTGAIAj4oda_5yP';\n\n// 获取 access_token\nfunction getAccessToken() {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const url = `https://api.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/token?grant_type=client_credential&appid=${WECHAT_APP_ID}&secret=${WECHAT_APP_SECRET}`;\n    \n    https.get(url, (res) => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        try {\n          const result = JSON.parse(data);\n          if (result.access_token) {\n            resolve(result.access_token);\n          } else {\n            reject(result);\n          }\n        } catch (e) {\n          reject(e);\n        }\n      });\n    }).on('error', reject);\n  });\n}\n\n// 发布草稿\nfunction publishDraft(accessToken) {\n  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n    const postData = JSON.stringify({ media_id: MEDIA_ID });\n    const options = {\n      hostname: 'api.weixin.qq.com',\n      path: `/cgi-bin/freepublish/submit?access_token=${accessToken}`,\n      method: 'POST',\n      headers: {\n        'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n        'Content-Length': Buffer.byteLength(postData)\n      }\n    };\n    \n    const req = https.request(options, (res) => {\n      let data = '';\n      res.on('data', chunk => data += chunk);\n      res.on('end', () => {\n        try {\n          resolve(JSON.parse(data));\n        } catch (e) {\n          reject(e);\n        }\n      });\n    });\n    \n    req.on('error', reject);\n    req.write(postData);\n    req.end();\n  });\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  try {\n    console.log('获取 access_token...');\n    const accessToken = await getAccessToken();\n    console.log('access_token 获取成功');\n    \n    console.log('发布草稿...');\n    const result = await publishDraft(accessToken);\n    console.log(JSON.stringify(result, null, 2));\n    \n    if (result.publish_id) {\n      console.log('\\n✅ 发布成功！');\n      console.log('publish_id:', result.publish_id);\n      console.log('msg_data_id:', result.msg_data_id);\n    } else {\n      console.log('\\n❌ 发布失败：', result);\n    }\n  } catch (error) {\n    console.error('错误：', error);\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\nEOF\nnode /tmp/publish-wechat.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773234750136}}
{"type":"message","id":"98e77fcc","parentId":"c5ec41cb","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:13:09.739Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-1f5b6c4d19864b2eaa034a58ebd9b72c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"获取 access_token...\naccess_token 获取成功\n发布草稿...\n{\n  \"errcode\": 48001,\n  \"errmsg\": \"api unauthorized rid: 69b16a65-037ad500-62e236fc\"\n}\n\n❌ 发布失败： {\n  errcode: 48001,\n  errmsg: 'api unauthorized rid: 69b16a65-037ad500-62e236fc'\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1038,"aggregated":"获取 access_token...\naccess_token 获取成功\n发布草稿...\n{\n  \"errcode\": 48001,\n  \"errmsg\": \"api unauthorized rid: 69b16a65-037ad500-62e236fc\"\n}\n\n❌ 发布失败： {\n  errcode: 48001,\n  errmsg: 'api unauthorized rid: 69b16a65-037ad500-62e236fc'\n}","cwd":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/media"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773234789730}}
{"type":"message","id":"d22a3bb5","parentId":"98e77fcc","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:13:17.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"发布失败了，错误是 48001 \"api unauthorized\"。这意味着当前的 API 凭证没有发布权限。\n\n让我检查一下可能的原因：\n1. API 凭证可能没有配置正确的权限\n2. 可能需要使用浏览器方式手动发布\n\n我应该告诉用户这个情况，并建议手动登录公众号后台发布。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发布失败，API 错误提示 `api unauthorized`（未授权）。\n\n这说明当前的 API 凭证没有发布权限。这种情况很常见，因为公众号 API 需要特定的高级接口权限才能发布。\n\n**建议操作**：\n\n1. **手动发布**（最可靠）：\n   - 登录 https://mp.weixin.qq.com\n   - 进入「内容管理」→「草稿箱」\n   - 找到文章：AI爆文拆解+多智能体协作，一人公司的内容生产模式\n   - 点击「发布」\n\n2. **浏览器自动化发布**（我帮你操作）：\n   - 打开 Chrome，自动登录公众号\n   - 自动点击发布流程\n\n你想让我用浏览器自动发布，还是你自己手动登录发布？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773234789738}}
{"type":"message","id":"56c94ed6","parentId":"d22a3bb5","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:13:55.847Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-11 21:13:55 GMT+8] Feishu[media] DM | 用户154215 (ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0) [msg:om_x100b5422e7e03cb4c2e27ff537e36ca]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5422e7e03cb4c2e27ff537e36ca\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户154215\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 21:13 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户154215 (ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0\",\n  \"name\": \"用户154215\"\n}\n```\n\n我登陆上了 你想办法自己完成发布 我后边也需要你直接发布"}],"timestamp":1773234835843}}
{"type":"message","id":"7efaa42f","parentId":"56c94ed6","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:14:05.442Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说已经登录了公众号，让我想办法自己完成发布，而且以后也需要我直接发布。这意味着用户希望有一个自动化的发布流程。\n\n由于 API 发布失败（权限问题），我需要使用浏览器自动化来完成发布。我可以使用 camofox 或者直接使用 Chrome CDP。\n\n让我检查一下 baoyu-post-to-wechat 技能中是否有浏览器发布草稿的功能。从之前读取的 SKILL.md 文件来看，有一个 `wechat-browser.ts` 脚本可以用于浏览器自动化。\n\n不过，我需要先确认：\n1. 用户已经登录了公众号\n2. 我可以使用浏览器自动化来点击发布按钮\n\n让我尝试使用 camofox 或者 Chrome CDP 来完成这个任务。首先，我应该使用 camofox_create_tab 打开公众号草稿箱页面，然后自动点击发布按钮。\n\n或者，我可以编写一个简单的脚本来使用 Chrome 的 CDP (Chrome DevTools Protocol) 来完成这个任务。\n\n让我先尝试使用 camofox 来打开公众号并完成发布流程。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我用浏览器自动化帮你发布。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-6539961464ef4eaba98127e3df8b351d","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"start"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773234835845}}
