{"type":"message","id":"ceb561be","parentId":"52aa5f0b","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:16:40.994Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"API 发布失败了，错误是 48001 (api unauthorized)。这说明当前的公众号凭证没有发布权限。这可能是因为：\n\n1. 当前是订阅号，而非服务号\n2. 公众号没有通过微信认证\n3. API 权限未开通\n\n我需要用浏览器自动化方式来完成发布。让我重新打开草稿箱页面，找到刚才上传的文章，然后模拟点击发布流程。\n\n首先，我需要清空搜索框，然后查看草稿箱第一页，看看新上传的文章是否在第一页。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看来 API 没有发布权限（可能是订阅号限制）。让我用浏览器自动化方式完成发布。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-a3d5d2a45d284b8283847af45ff94991","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetId":"FEB282C3FD54D410BE73EA55E0B2A73B","url":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/appmsg?t=media/appmsg_edit_v2&action=list&listType=0&type=10&begin=0&count=10&lang=zh_CN&token=1836899681"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773234985184}}
