{"type":"message","id":"319bca5b","parentId":"e3953835","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:27:26.806Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要增加原创文章创作的功能，让我先检查一下可用的技能列表。\n\n从之前的技能列表中，我看到有一些相关的技能：\n\n1. baoyu-format-markdown - Markdown 格式化\n2. baoyu-translate - 翻译\n3. baoyu-url-to-markdown - 网页抓取\n4. baoyu-article-illustrator - 文章配图\n5. baoyu-infographic - 信息图\n6. baoyu-xhs-images - 小红书信息图\n\n但是没有专门的\"原创文章创作\"技能。让我看看有没有其他相关的工具或脚本。\n\n我需要：\n1. 检查技能目录中是否有相关技能\n2. 查看 AGENTS.md 中是否有相关信息\n3. 搜索现有工具\n\n让我先检查一下可用的技能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！让我检查一下现有的技能中是否有原创文章创作相关的功能。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-14b2d421ad4e4fc5b73446356c87d5fc","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/extensions -name \"SKILL.md\" -type f | xargs grep -l \"文章\\|创作\\|写作\\|生成\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773235638922}}
