{"type":"message","id":"17bebc1c","parentId":"9f072538","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:28:10.137Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-7c817ac6c78d4e5c82c7030a8cfffe67","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== baoyu-danger-gemini-web ===\n---\nname: baoyu-danger-gemini-web\ndescription: Generates images and text via reverse-engineered Gemini Web API. Supports text generation, image generation from prompts, reference images for vision input, and multi-turn conversations. Use when other skills need image generation backend, or when user requests \"generate image with Gemini\", \"Gemini text generation\", or needs vision-capable AI generation.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown ===\n---\nname: baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown\ndescription: Converts X (Twitter) tweets and articles to markdown with YAML front matter. Uses reverse-engineered API requiring user consent. Use when user mentions \"X to markdown\", \"tweet to markdown\", \"save tweet\", or provides x.com/twitter.com URLs for conversion.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-format-markdown ===\n---\nname: baoyu-format-markdown\ndescription: Formats plain text or markdown files with frontmatter, titles, summaries, headings, bold, lists, and code blocks. Use when user asks to \"format markdown\", \"beautify article\", \"add formatting\", or improve article layout. Outputs to {filename}-formatted.md.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-image-gen ===\n---\nname: baoyu-image-gen\ndescription: AI image generation with OpenAI, Google, DashScope and Replicate APIs. Supports text-to-image, reference images, aspect ratios. Sequential by default; parallel generation available on request. Use when user asks to generate, create, or draw images.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-infographic ===\n---\nname: baoyu-infographic\ndescription: Generates professional infographics with 21 layout types and 20 visual styles. Analyzes content, recommends layout×style combinations, and generates publication-ready infographics. Use when user asks to create \"infographic\", \"信息图\", \"visual summary\", \"可视化\", or \"高密度信息大图\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-markdown-to-html ===\n---\nname: baoyu-markdown-to-html\ndescription: Converts Markdown to styled HTML with WeChat-compatible themes. Supports code highlighting, math, PlantUML, footnotes, alerts, and infographics. Use when user asks for \"markdown to html\", \"convert md to html\", \"md转html\", or needs styled HTML output from markdown.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-post-to-wechat ===\n---\nname: baoyu-post-to-wechat\ndescription: Posts content to WeChat Official Account (微信公众号) via API or Chrome CDP. Supports article posting (文章) with HTML, markdown, or plain text input, and image-text posting (贴图, formerly 图文) with multiple images. Use when user mentions \"发布公众号\", \"post to wechat\", \"微信公众号\", or \"贴图/图文/文章\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-post-to-weibo ===\n---\nname: baoyu-post-to-weibo\ndescription: Posts content to Weibo (微博). Supports regular posts with text, images, and videos, and headline articles (头条文章) with Markdown input via Chrome CDP. Use when user asks to \"post to Weibo\", \"发微博\", \"发布微博\", \"publish to Weibo\", \"share on Weibo\", \"写微博\", or \"微博头条文章\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-post-to-x ===\n---\nname: baoyu-post-to-x\ndescription: Posts content and articles to X (Twitter). Supports regular posts with images/videos and X Articles (long-form Markdown). Uses real Chrome with CDP to bypass anti-automation. Use when user asks to \"post to X\", \"tweet\", \"publish to Twitter\", or \"share on X\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-slide-deck ===\n---\nname: baoyu-slide-deck\ndescription: Generates professional slide deck images from content. Creates outlines with style instructions, then generates individual slide images. Use when user asks to \"create slides\", \"make a presentation\", \"generate deck\", \"slide deck\", or \"PPT\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-translate ===\n---\nname: baoyu-translate\ndescription: Translates articles and documents between languages with three modes - quick (direct), normal (analyze then translate), and refined (analyze, translate, review, polish). Supports custom glossaries and terminology consistency via EXTEND.md. Use when user asks to \"translate\", \"翻译\", \"精翻\", \"translate article\", \"translate to Chinese/English\", \"改成中文\", \"改成英文\", \"convert to Chinese\", \"localize\", \"本地化\", or needs any document translation. Also triggers for \"refined translation\", \"精细翻译\", \"proofread translation\", \"快速翻译\", \"快翻\", \"这篇文章翻译一下\", or when a URL or file is provided with translation intent.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-url-to-markdown ===\n---\nname: baoyu-url-to-markdown\ndescription: Fetch any URL and convert to markdown using Chrome CDP. Saves the rendered HTML snapshot alongside the markdown, and automatically falls back to the pre-Defuddle HTML-to-Markdown pipeline when Defuddle fails. Supports two modes - auto-capture on page load, or wait for user signal (for pages requiring login). Use when user wants to save a webpage as markdown.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-xhs-images ===\n---\nname: baoyu-xhs-images\ndescription: Generates Xiaohongshu (Little Red Book) infographic series with 10 visual styles and 8 layouts. Breaks content into 1-10 cartoon-style images optimized for XHS engagement. Use when user mentions \"小红书图片\", \"XHS images\", \"RedNote infographics\", \"小红书种草\", or wants social media infographics for Chinese platforms.\n---\n\n\n=== release-skills ===\n---\nname: release-skills\ndescription: Universal release workflow. Auto-detects version files and changelogs. Supports Node.js, Python, Rust, Claude Plugin, and generic projects. Use when user says \"release\", \"发布\", \"new version\", \"bump version\", \"push\", \"推送\".\n---"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":212,"aggregated":"=== baoyu-danger-gemini-web ===\n---\nname: baoyu-danger-gemini-web\ndescription: Generates images and text via reverse-engineered Gemini Web API. Supports text generation, image generation from prompts, reference images for vision input, and multi-turn conversations. Use when other skills need image generation backend, or when user requests \"generate image with Gemini\", \"Gemini text generation\", or needs vision-capable AI generation.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown ===\n---\nname: baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown\ndescription: Converts X (Twitter) tweets and articles to markdown with YAML front matter. Uses reverse-engineered API requiring user consent. Use when user mentions \"X to markdown\", \"tweet to markdown\", \"save tweet\", or provides x.com/twitter.com URLs for conversion.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-format-markdown ===\n---\nname: baoyu-format-markdown\ndescription: Formats plain text or markdown files with frontmatter, titles, summaries, headings, bold, lists, and code blocks. Use when user asks to \"format markdown\", \"beautify article\", \"add formatting\", or improve article layout. Outputs to {filename}-formatted.md.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-image-gen ===\n---\nname: baoyu-image-gen\ndescription: AI image generation with OpenAI, Google, DashScope and Replicate APIs. Supports text-to-image, reference images, aspect ratios. Sequential by default; parallel generation available on request. Use when user asks to generate, create, or draw images.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-infographic ===\n---\nname: baoyu-infographic\ndescription: Generates professional infographics with 21 layout types and 20 visual styles. Analyzes content, recommends layout×style combinations, and generates publication-ready infographics. Use when user asks to create \"infographic\", \"信息图\", \"visual summary\", \"可视化\", or \"高密度信息大图\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-markdown-to-html ===\n---\nname: baoyu-markdown-to-html\ndescription: Converts Markdown to styled HTML with WeChat-compatible themes. Supports code highlighting, math, PlantUML, footnotes, alerts, and infographics. Use when user asks for \"markdown to html\", \"convert md to html\", \"md转html\", or needs styled HTML output from markdown.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-post-to-wechat ===\n---\nname: baoyu-post-to-wechat\ndescription: Posts content to WeChat Official Account (微信公众号) via API or Chrome CDP. Supports article posting (文章) with HTML, markdown, or plain text input, and image-text posting (贴图, formerly 图文) with multiple images. Use when user mentions \"发布公众号\", \"post to wechat\", \"微信公众号\", or \"贴图/图文/文章\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-post-to-weibo ===\n---\nname: baoyu-post-to-weibo\ndescription: Posts content to Weibo (微博). Supports regular posts with text, images, and videos, and headline articles (头条文章) with Markdown input via Chrome CDP. Use when user asks to \"post to Weibo\", \"发微博\", \"发布微博\", \"publish to Weibo\", \"share on Weibo\", \"写微博\", or \"微博头条文章\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-post-to-x ===\n---\nname: baoyu-post-to-x\ndescription: Posts content and articles to X (Twitter). Supports regular posts with images/videos and X Articles (long-form Markdown). Uses real Chrome with CDP to bypass anti-automation. Use when user asks to \"post to X\", \"tweet\", \"publish to Twitter\", or \"share on X\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-slide-deck ===\n---\nname: baoyu-slide-deck\ndescription: Generates professional slide deck images from content. Creates outlines with style instructions, then generates individual slide images. Use when user asks to \"create slides\", \"make a presentation\", \"generate deck\", \"slide deck\", or \"PPT\".\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-translate ===\n---\nname: baoyu-translate\ndescription: Translates articles and documents between languages with three modes - quick (direct), normal (analyze then translate), and refined (analyze, translate, review, polish). Supports custom glossaries and terminology consistency via EXTEND.md. Use when user asks to \"translate\", \"翻译\", \"精翻\", \"translate article\", \"translate to Chinese/English\", \"改成中文\", \"改成英文\", \"convert to Chinese\", \"localize\", \"本地化\", or needs any document translation. Also triggers for \"refined translation\", \"精细翻译\", \"proofread translation\", \"快速翻译\", \"快翻\", \"这篇文章翻译一下\", or when a URL or file is provided with translation intent.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-url-to-markdown ===\n---\nname: baoyu-url-to-markdown\ndescription: Fetch any URL and convert to markdown using Chrome CDP. Saves the rendered HTML snapshot alongside the markdown, and automatically falls back to the pre-Defuddle HTML-to-Markdown pipeline when Defuddle fails. Supports two modes - auto-capture on page load, or wait for user signal (for pages requiring login). Use when user wants to save a webpage as markdown.\n---\n\n\n=== baoyu-xhs-images ===\n---\nname: baoyu-xhs-images\ndescription: Generates Xiaohongshu (Little Red Book) infographic series with 10 visual styles and 8 layouts. Breaks content into 1-10 cartoon-style images optimized for XHS engagement. Use when user mentions \"小红书图片\", \"XHS images\", \"RedNote infographics\", \"小红书种草\", or wants social media infographics for Chinese platforms.\n---\n\n\n=== release-skills ===\n---\nname: release-skills\ndescription: Universal release workflow. Auto-detects version files and changelogs. Supports Node.js, Python, Rust, Claude Plugin, and generic projects. Use when user says \"release\", \"发布\", \"new version\", \"bump version\", \"push\", \"推送\".\n---","cwd":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/media"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773235690130}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f01305a","parentId":"17bebc1c","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:28:23.300Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我查看一下 `baoyu-danger-gemini-web` 技能，它支持文本生成，可能可以用于原创文章创作。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-865d414390f949419c2c2c409260fa00","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/media/.agents/skills/baoyu-danger-gemini-web/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773235690136}}
{"type":"message","id":"42da31ac","parentId":"2f01305a","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:28:23.314Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"tool-865d414390f949419c2c2c409260fa00","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: baoyu-danger-gemini-web\ndescription: Generates images and text via reverse-engineered Gemini Web API. Supports text generation, image generation from prompts, reference images for vision input, and multi-turn conversations. Use when other skills need image generation backend, or when user requests \"generate image with Gemini\", \"Gemini text generation\", or needs vision-capable AI generation.\n---\n\n# Gemini Web Client\n\nText/image generation via Gemini Web API. Supports reference images and multi-turn conversations.\n\n## Script Directory\n\n**Important**: All scripts are located in the `scripts/` subdirectory of this skill.\n\n**Agent Execution Instructions**:\n1. Determine this SKILL.md file's directory path as `SKILL_DIR`\n2. Script path = `${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/<script-name>.ts`\n3. Resolve `${BUN_X}` runtime: if `bun` installed → `bun`; if `npx` available → `npx -y bun`; else suggest installing bun\n4. Replace all `${SKILL_DIR}` and `${BUN_X}` in this document with actual values\n\n**Script Reference**:\n| Script | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `scripts/main.ts` | CLI entry point for text/image generation |\n| `scripts/gemini-webapi/*` | TypeScript port of `gemini_webapi` (GeminiClient, types, utils) |\n\n## Consent Check (REQUIRED)\n\nBefore first use, verify user consent for reverse-engineered API usage.\n\n**Consent file locations**:\n- macOS: `~/Library/Application Support/baoyu-skills/gemini-web/consent.json`\n- Linux: `~/.local/share/baoyu-skills/gemini-web/consent.json`\n- Windows: `%APPDATA%\\baoyu-skills\\gemini-web\\consent.json`\n\n**Flow**:\n1. Check if consent file exists with `accepted: true` and `disclaimerVersion: \"1.0\"`\n2. If valid consent exists → print warning with `acceptedAt` date, proceed\n3. If no consent → show disclaimer, ask user via `AskUserQuestion`:\n   - \"Yes, I accept\" → create consent file with ISO timestamp, proceed\n   - \"No, I decline\" → output decline message, stop\n4. Consent file format: `{\"version\":1,\"accepted\":true,\"acceptedAt\":\"<ISO>\",\"disclaimerVersion\":\"1.0\"}`\n\n---\n\n## Preferences (EXTEND.md)\n\nCheck EXTEND.md existence (priority order):\n\n```bash\n# macOS, Linux, WSL, Git Bash\ntest -f .baoyu-skills/baoyu-danger-gemini-web/EXTEND.md && echo \"project\"\ntest -f \"$HOME/.baoyu-skills/baoyu-danger-gemini-web/EXTEND.md\" && echo \"user\"\n```\n\n```powershell\n# PowerShell (Windows)\nif (Test-Path .baoyu-skills/baoyu-danger-gemini-web/EXTEND.md) { \"project\" }\nif (Test-Path \"$HOME/.baoyu-skills/baoyu-danger-gemini-web/EXTEND.md\") { \"user\" }\n```\n\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────┐\n│                           Path                           │     Location      │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────┤\n│ .baoyu-skills/baoyu-danger-gemini-web/EXTEND.md          │ Project directory │\n├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼───────────────────┤\n│ $HOME/.baoyu-skills/baoyu-danger-gemini-web/EXTEND.md    │ User home         │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┴───────────────────┘\n\n┌───────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Result   │                                  Action                                   │\n├───────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Found     │ Read, parse, apply settings                                               │\n├───────────┼───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│ Not found │ Use defaults                                                              │\n└───────────┴───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n**EXTEND.md Supports**: Default model | Proxy settings | Custom data directory\n\n## Usage\n\n```bash\n# Text generation\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts \"Your prompt\"\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts --prompt \"Your prompt\" --model gemini-3-flash\n\n# Image generation\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts --prompt \"A cute cat\" --image cat.png\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts --promptfiles system.md content.md --image out.png\n\n# Vision input (reference images)\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts --prompt \"Describe this\" --reference image.png\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts --prompt \"Create variation\" --reference a.png --image out.png\n\n# Multi-turn conversation\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts \"Remember: 42\" --sessionId session-abc\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts \"What number?\" --sessionId session-abc\n\n# JSON output\n${BUN_X} ${SKILL_DIR}/scripts/main.ts \"Hello\" --json\n```\n\n## Options\n\n| Option | Description |\n|--------|-------------|\n| `--prompt`, `-p` | Prompt text |\n| `--promptfiles` | Read prompt from files (concatenated) |\n| `--model`, `-m` | Model: gemini-3-pro (default), gemini-3-flash, gemini-3-flash-thinking, gemini-3.1-pro-preview |\n| `--image [path]` | Generate image (default: generated.png) |\n| `--reference`, `--ref` | Reference images for vision input |\n| `--sessionId` | Session ID for multi-turn conversation |\n| `--list-sessions` | List saved sessions |\n| `--json` | Output as JSON |\n| `--login` | Refresh cookies, then exit |\n| `--cookie-path` | Custom cookie file path |\n| `--profile-dir` | Chrome profile directory |\n\n## Models\n\n| Model | Description |\n|-------|-------------|\n| `gemini-3-pro` | Default, latest 3.0 Pro |\n| `gemini-3-flash` | Fast, lightweight 3.0 Flash |\n| `gemini-3-flash-thinking` | 3.0 Flash with thinking |\n| `gemini-3.1-pro-preview` | 3.1 Pro preview (empty header, auto-routed) |\n\n## Authentication\n\nFirst run opens browser for Google auth. Cookies cached automatically.\n\nSupported browsers (auto-detected): Chrome, Chrome Canary/Beta, Chromium, Edge.\n\nForce refresh: `--login` flag. Override browser: `GEMINI_WEB_CHROME_PATH` env var.\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Description |\n|----------|-------------|\n| `GEMINI_WEB_DATA_DIR` | Data directory |\n| `GEMINI_WEB_COOKIE_PATH` | Cookie file path |\n| `GEMINI_WEB_CHROME_PROFILE_DIR` | Chrome profile directory |\n| `GEMINI_WEB_CHROME_PATH` | Chrome executable path |\n| `HTTP_PROXY`, `HTTPS_PROXY` | Proxy for Google access (set inline with command) |\n\n## Sessions\n\nSession files stored in data directory under `sessions/<id>.json`.\n\nContains: `id`, `metadata` (Gemini chat state), `messages` array, timestamps.\n\n## Extension Support\n\nCustom configurations via EXTEND.md. See **Preferences** section for paths and supported options.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773235703304}}
{"type":"message","id":"d7fb9b65","parentId":"42da31ac","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:28:50.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，用户想要增加原创文章创作的功能。让我检查一下现有的技能。\n\n从技能列表来看，现有的技能主要包括：\n\n1. **内容整理类**：\n   - baoyu-format-markdown - 格式化 Markdown\n   - baoyu-markdown-to-html - Markdown 转 HTML\n   - baoyu-translate - 翻译文章\n\n2. **内容生成类**：\n   - baoyu-danger-gemini-web - Gemini 文本/图像生成（支持文本生成）\n   - baoyu-image-gen - AI 图像生成\n   - baoyu-comic - 知识漫画创作\n   - baoyu-infographic - 信息图生成\n   - baoyu-slide-deck - 幻灯片生成\n\n3. **内容获取类**：\n   - baoyu-danger-x-to-markdown - X 推文转 Markdown\n   - baoyu-url-to-markdown - 网页转 Markdown\n\n4. **内容发布类**：\n   - baoyu-post-to-wechat - 发布到公众号\n   - baoyu-post-to-weibo - 发布到微博\n   - baoyu-post-to-x - 发布到 X\n\n5. **辅助类**：\n   - baoyu-cover-image - 封面图生成\n   - baoyu-xhs-images - 小红书图片生成\n   - baoyu-article-illustrator - 文章配图\n   - baoyu-compress-image - 图片压缩\n\n从这些技能来看，**没有专门用于原创文章创作的技能**。\n\n现有的技能主要集中在：\n- 内容格式化和排版\n\n\n- 翻译功能\n- 多媒体内容生成\n\n目前缺乏一个完整的原创文章创作工具。需要考虑整合现有能力，开发一个新的综合性文章创作技能。关键是要支持从灵感到发布的全流程，包括选题、大纲、写作和润色等环节。\n\n将利用 Gemini Web 的文本生成能力作为核心技术，设计一个灵活且强大的文章生成解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来检查一下现有的创作相关技能。\n\n## 📊 现有技能分析\n\n根据检查，现有技能中与内容创作相关的有：\n\n### ✅ 已有的创作支持技能\n\n1. **baoyu-danger-gemini-web** - Gemini 文本生成\n   - 支持文本生成（gemini-3-pro/flash）\n   - 支持多轮对话\n   - 支持视觉输入\n\n2. **baoyu-translate** - 翻译和润色\n   - 支持快速翻译\n   - 支持精细翻译（分析→翻译→审校→润色）\n\n3. **baoyu-format-markdown** - 格式化\n   - 添加 frontmatter、标题、摘要\n   - 优化段落、列表、代码块\n\n### ❌ 缺失的功能\n\n**没有专门的原创文章创作技能**！\n\n现有的技能：\n- ✅ 能生成文本片段\n- ✅ 能翻译和润色\n- ✅ 能格式化和排版\n- ❌ 缺少完整的文章创作流程\n- ❌ 缺少选题和大纲生成\n- ❌ 缺少写作指导\n\n---\n\n## 💡 原创文章创作功能建议\n\n我可以为你创建一个新的技能：**baoyu-article-creator**，功能包括：\n\n### 核心功能\n\n1. **选题生成**\n   - 根据领域/关键词生成选题\n   - 分析热点趋势\n   - 推荐爆款选题方向\n\n2. **大纲生成**\n   - 自动生成文章大纲\n   - 结构化章节设计\n   - 知识点梳理\n\n3. **正文创作**\n   - 根据大纲生成正文\n   - 保持风格一致性\n   - 支持多轮迭代优化\n\n4. **内容润色**\n   - 优化语言表达\n   - 增强逻辑连贯性\n   - 提升可读性\n\n5. **质量检测**\n   - AI 检测率分析\n   - 同质化检查\n   - 可读性评分\n\n### 工作流程\n\n```\n用户输入主题/关键词\n    ↓\n选题生成（可选）\n    ↓\n大纲生成\n    ↓\n正文创作\n    ↓\n内容润色\n    ↓\n格式化输出\n    ↓\n发布准备（封面图、摘要等）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 实现方案\n\n我可以为你创建这个技能，需要确认：\n\n1. **功能优先级**\n   - 基础版：选题 + 大纲 + 正文生成\n   - 完整版：+ 润色 + 质量检测 + 风格定制\n\n2. **集成方式**\n   - 独立技能（手动调用）\n   - 自动化工作流（一键完成）\n\n3. **使用场景**\n   - 从零开始创作\n   - 基于素材扩展\n   - 翻改现有文章\n\n需要我现在开始创建这个技能吗？📱"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773235703313}}
{"type":"message","id":"d5415abd","parentId":"d7fb9b65","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:30:06.258Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-11 21:30:05 GMT+8] Feishu[media] DM | 用户154215 (ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0) [msg:om_x100b5422ab0b74a8c4e9237c1ed23d2]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5422ab0b74a8c4e9237c1ed23d2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户154215\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-11 21:30 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户154215 (ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_3663708102e58eeceb009472194555f0\",\n  \"name\": \"用户154215\"\n}\n```\n\n这个技能 能确保创作的文章的可读性和真实性吗"}],"timestamp":1773235806247}}
{"type":"message","id":"e06ceb67","parentId":"d5415abd","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:30:34.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是关于原创文章创作技能能否确保可读性和真实性。这是个很好的问题，涉及到AI生成内容的质量控制。\n\n让我分析一下：\n\n1. **可读性**：\n   - AI生成的文章容易出现AI味\n   - 可能机械化、重复\n   - 需要避免\"正确的废话\"\n\n2. **真实性**：\n   - AI可能会产生幻觉（虚构信息）\n   - 需要事实核查\n   - 需要引用来源\n\n现有的baoyu-danger-gemini-web技能支持文本生成，但不能保证质量。如果要创建新的技能，需要考虑：\n\n1. **质量控制机制**：\n   - 多轮迭代优化\n   - 可读性评分\n   - AI检测率分析\n\n2. **真实性保障**：\n   - 引用来源\n   - 事实核查\n   - 避免虚构信息\n\n3. **人工介入**：\n   - 终审机制\n   - 用户确认\n   - 可编辑修改\n\n我应该诚实地告诉用户：AI不能100%保证可读性和真实性，但可以通过机制来提高质量。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这是个非常重要的问题！让我坦诚地分析一下：\n\n## ⚠️ AI 创作的局限性\n\n### 1. **可读性问题**\n\n**常见问题**：\n- ✗ AI味重（机械化表达）\n- ✗ 重复冗余（正确的废话）\n- ✗ 缺少个人风格\n- ✗ 逻辑不够自然\n\n**原因**：\n- AI 模型训练数据偏差\n- 缺少具体语境\n- 缺少风格化训练\n\n### 2. **真实性问题**\n\n**常见问题**：\n- ✗ 幻觉（虚构事实）\n- ✗ 过时信息（训练数据时效性）\n- ✗ 缺少引用来源\n- ✗ 数据不准确\n\n**原因**：\n- AI 不理解\"真实\"，只懂\"概率\"\n- 缺少实时数据\n- 缺少事实核查机制\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 质量保障机制（可实现）\n\n虽然不能 100% 保证，但可以通过以下机制大幅提升质量：\n\n### 1. **可读性保障**\n\n**多轮迭代优化**：\n```\n初稿 → AI检测 → 可读性评分 → 优化 → 再评分 → 输出\n```\n\n**具体措施**：\n- 使用\"反AI味\"提示词\n- 模拟真实写作风格\n- 增加个人化表达\n- 优化段落节奏\n\n**参考**：你之前转发的文章提到\"构建专属知识库\"，就是把个人风格输入给 AI。\n\n### 2. **真实性保障**\n\n**事实核查**：\n- 要求 AI 标注信息来源\n- 标注\"不确定\"的内容\n- 提供参考资料链接\n\n**内容验证**：\n- 避免绝对化表述（\"一定\"、\"必然\"）\n- 使用谨慎语气（\"可能\"、\"据研究\"）\n- 区分事实和观点\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 实际建议\n\n### 如果创建原创创作技能，我会加入：\n\n1. **质量检测模块**\n   ```typescript\n   interface QualityCheck {\n     readability: number;      // 可读性评分 (0-100)\n     aiDetection: number;      // AI检测率 (0-100%)\n     authenticity: number;      // 真实性评分 (0-100)\n     suggestions: string[];     // 优化建议\n   }\n   ```\n\n2. **风格化模板**\n   ```typescript\n   interface StyleProfile {\n     tone: \"formal\" | \"casual\" | \"humorous\";\n     length: \"short\" | \"medium\" | \"long\";\n     structure: \"listicle\" | \"narrative\" | \"tutorial\";\n     personalVoice: boolean;  // 是否注入个人风格\n   }\n   ```\n\n3. **人工确认流程**\n   - 生成初稿 → 质量检测 → 用户确认 → 最终输出\n   - 支持人工编辑修改\n   - 支持多轮迭代\n\n---\n\n## 💡 我的建议\n\n### 短期方案（现在就能做）：\n\n1. **利用现有技能组合**：\n   - baoyu-danger-gemini-web（文本生成）\n   - baoyu-format-markdown（格式化）\n   - 手动审核修改\n\n2. **提示词工程**：\n   - 加入\"避免AI味\"指令\n   - 要求\"具体案例和数据\"\n   - 要求\"个人化表达\"\n\n### 长期方案（可开发）：\n\n1. **创建 baoyu-article-creator 技能**\n   - 内置质量检测机制\n   - 风格化模板系统\n   - 多轮迭代优化\n\n2. **知识库集成**\n   - 存储个人写作风格\n   - 存储领域知识\n   - 存储写作规范\n\n---\n\n## 🤔 直接回答你的问题\n\n**能确保可读性和真实性吗？**\n\n- **不能 100% 确保**，但可以**大幅提升**（预计 70-85% 质量）\n- **需要人工介入**：终审、事实核查、风格调整\n- **需要持续优化**：根据反馈调整提示词和模板\n\n**最可靠的方式**：\n1. AI 生成初稿\n2. 质量检测和评分\n3. 人工审核修改\n4. 最终确认发布\n\n---\n\n需要我现在开始创建这个技能吗？还是先用现有工具试一下效果？📱"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773235806252}}
