{"type":"message","id":"f17c162e","parentId":"2376d617","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:43:25.409Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想按顺序测试这 3 个新技能。让我先从第一个开始：wechat-article。\n\n我可以给用户一个测试用例，比如提供一个公众号文章链接，然后用 wechat-article 技能抓取内容。\n\n或者，我可以先用一个实际的案例来测试。让我想想什么方式比较好。\n\n对于 wechat-article，我可以：\n1. 使用一个公众号文章链接（比如刚才发布的文章）\n2. 运行脚本抓取\n3. 展示结果\n\n对于 blog-writer，我可以：\n1. 给定一个主题\n2. 使用技能写一篇小媒风格的文章\n3. 展示结果\n\n对于 humanizer，我可以：\n1. 用 Gemini 生成一段有明显 AI 味的文字\n2. 用 humanizer 处理\n3. 对比前后效果\n\n让我开始吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我们按顺序测试这 3 个技能。\n\n## 🧪 测试 1/3：wechat-article（公众号文章抓取）\n\n让我测试刚才发布的文章："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-339a243231544c939c74281ba98a0a33","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/media/skills/wechat-article/scripts/wechat_article.py \"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/28C-5DPdg-8NqCV-t-3Hjw\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773236579610}}
