{"type":"message","id":"2dd89dbb","parentId":"2e763228","timestamp":"2026-03-11T13:46:27.166Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我已经创建了一个 humanizer 的版本。现在让我对比一下：\n\n**AI 版本**：\n- 346 字\n- 典型 AI 味重（inflated symbolism、rule of three、AI vocabulary）\n- 没有个人视角\n- 没有具体案例\n\n**Humanized 版本**：\n- 421 字\n- 有\"我\"的第一人称视角\n- 有具体案例（同事用 Claude、ChatGPT、Midjourney）\n- 有个人感受\n- 句式有变化（长短句结合）\n- 有对话感\n\n现在我继续测试 blog-writer。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**测试 2 结果**：✅ 成功\n- AI 原文：346 字，AI 味重，没有个性\n- Humanized 后：421 字，有个人视角，有具体案例，有对话感\n\n---\n\n## 🧪 测试 3/3：blog-writer（博客写手）\n\nblog-writer 需要用户明确要求才会触发。让我用一个小媒风格的主题测试：\n\n让我先查看一下 blog-writer 的结构："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-ed1ee34cdb4f4f238e502ede0a9247ee","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/media/skills/blog-writer/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773236777966}}
