{"type":"message","id":"936db9d5","parentId":"51f7453e","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:15:42.385Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户提供了飞书应用的 App ID 和 App Secret。我还需要 Encrypt Key，但用户没有提供。让我先配置已有的信息，然后提醒用户还需要 Encrypt Key。\n\n另外，Webhook URL 是 loopback 模式，只支持本机访问。如果用户需要外网访问，需要修改配置。让我先完成基础配置，然后提醒用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我现在帮你配置小猎的飞书账号。\n\n但是我还需要 **Encrypt Key**（加密密钥），这个是在飞书开放平台\"事件订阅\"页面自动生成的。\n\n让我先配置已有信息，然后提醒你获取 Encrypt Key："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool-b8a06fda0ebf4c73a57543cd8cb8d6db","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json | jq '.channels.feishu.accounts.hunter = {\"appId\": \"cli_a93bc48d75b8dbce\", \"appSecret\": \"44r9DLzKHkTAUMseTM1itbKcV5XXgFhX\"}' > /tmp/openclaw-feishu-updated.json && mv /tmp/openclaw-feishu-updated.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json && echo \"✅ 飞书账号已配置\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773238537251}}
