t\": \"5fThCqKr3xBUwTwTUFe45cNvSvLHrRJt\",\n      \"input\": {\n        \"length\": {\n          \"max\": 150000,\n          \"min\": 1\n        },\n        \"filter\": {\n          \"empty\": true,\n          \"whitespace\": true\n        },\n        \"truncate\": {\n          \"enabled\": true,\n          \"maxLength\": 149999\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    \"hunter\": {\n      \"appId\": \"cli_a93bc48d75b8dbce\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"44r9DLzKHkTAUMseTM1itbKcV5XXgFhX\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"bots\": [\n    {\n      \"app_id\": \"cli_a922eb10d3345bd9\",\n      \"app_secret\": \"RmuIQUydfwh3s2sMYyaPCgG0a0PNWDvq\",\n      \"agent_id\": \"writer\",\n      \"webhook_enabled\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"app_id\": \"cli_a92173401c385bc0\",\n      \"app_secret\": \"5fThCqKr3xBUwTwTUFe45cNvSvLHrRJt\",\n      \"agent_id\": \"media\",\n      \"webhook_enabled\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"app_id\": \"cli_a93bc48d75b8dbce\",\n      \"app_secret\": \"44r9DLzKHkTAUMseTM1itbKcV5XXgFhX\",\n      \"agent_id\": \"hunter\",\n      \"webhook_enabled\": true\n    }\n  ],\n  \"defaultAccount\": \"writer\"\n}","cwd":"/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/media"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773238548452}}
{"type":"message","id":"a5b80b54","parentId":"1096f8f1","timestamp":"2026-03-11T14:15:56.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！我已经成功配置了小猎的飞书账号和机器人。现在我需要提醒用户还需要添加 Encrypt Key。\n\n但是，查看当前配置，我没有看到 encryptKey 的配置。让我检查一下是否需要在配置中添加 encryptKey。\n\n根据之前的配置，可能需要在 accounts 配置中添加 encryptKey。让我先告诉用户当前配置已完成，然后提醒需要添加 Encrypt Key。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ 飞书配置已完成！\n\n我已经成功将小猎添加到飞书配置：\n\n### 配置内容\n\n**1. Agent 列表** ✅\n- hunter - 小猎\n- workspace: `/Users/wh1ko/Documents/openclaw/agents/hunter`\n- model: `bailian/qwen3.5-plus`\n\n**2. 飞书账号** ✅\n- appId: `cli_a93bc48d75b8dbce`\n- appSecret: `44r9DLzKHkTAUMseTM1itbKcV5XXgFhX`\n\n**3. 飞书机器人** ✅\n- app_id: `cli_a93bc48d75b8dbce`\n- app_secret: `44r9DLzKHkTAUMseTM1itbKcV5XXgFhX`\n- agent_id: `hunter`\n- webhook_enabled: `true`\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 还需要：添加 Encrypt Key\n\n配置基本完成，但还需要添加 **Encrypt Key** 才能正常工作。\n\n### 获取 Encrypt Key 步骤：\n\n1. **打开飞书开放平台**\n   - 访问：https://open.feishu.cn/app\n   - 找到小猎应用\n\n2. **进入事件订阅**\n   - 左侧菜单选择\"事件订阅\"\n   - 在\"Encrypt Key\"部分，你会看到一个自动生成的密钥\n\n3. **复制 Encrypt Key**\n   - 复制这个密钥\n\n4. **告诉我 Encrypt Key**\n   - 发送给小媒：`Encrypt Key: xxxxxxxxxx`\n\n---\n\n## 🔄 需要重启 Gateway 吗？\n\n如果你已经拿到了 Encrypt Key，告诉我，我会：\n1. 添加 Encrypt Key 到配置\n2. 重启 OpenClaw Gateway 使配置生效\n3. 验证小猎是否正常运行\n\n需要我继续吗？📱"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773238548461}}
